{"tid":1141714,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡有冇平靚正嘢食推介","createTime":"2019-05-06T16:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T01:36:52.000Z","uid":51738,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a6eb2a6fc4e7a665cdda89e2bd1dff5b130a2adf","tid":1141714,"uid":51738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:01:36.000Z","msg":"去新加坡旅行主要都係食玩瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時plan 啲行程都係以食為主<br />\n- 加東喇沙<br />\n- 結霜喇沙<br />\n- 天天海南雞飯<br />\n- 魚片頭粉<br />\n（對肉骨茶冇乜興趣）<br />\n<br />\n以上幾款都係算平又正嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於辣椒蟹、麥皮蝦、沙嗲串燒呢啲睇落都會幾貴，但又好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴絲打有冇價廉物美嘅餐廳推介可以食到呢啲菜式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24adb91775f296795a666cac6e663d0941dfd047","tid":1141714,"uid":72177,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:02:21.000Z","msg":"天天真係吹得好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b21208df5741bda8b40436e26ac36c09064599","tid":1141714,"uid":51738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24adb91775f296795a666cac6e663d0941dfd047","tid":1141714,"uid":72177,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:02:21.000Z","msg":"天天真係吹得好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:05:16.000Z","msg":"海南雞有冇其他舖推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4834d059612dafd27c50f75fce1360b16a45d32","tid":1141714,"uid":187295,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:59:09.000Z","msg":"松發肉骨茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78a9bc2c77c92392a457aba836de7d30d35d92d","tid":1141714,"uid":98401,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"48b21208df5741bda8b40436e26ac36c09064599","tid":1141